      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAYE VALENTINE (1) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when second (22.64) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning five races. Can go on with it. FLAMING FOX (2) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (22.85) at this track over 400m. Expected to feature. OREGON HUTAN (3) boasts a consistent overall record including 15 wins from 53 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (23.26) over 400m at Gawler. Form at the trip sound including 10 wins. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. PAW KARSON (7) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
